<h1>Welcome to Happy Feathers Hospital and Rehabilitation's (HFHR) official Patient Records Database Website! Above
    listed are our pages to interact with our database. Bellow you'll find descriptions of each page, and a button to reset the database!</h1>
<ul>
    <li><strong>View Birds:</strong> View all bird patients currently admitted to HFHR. Updating and Deleting is in
        here.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Bird:</strong> Add a new bird patient to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>View Species:</strong> View all bird species recognized by HFHR. Updating and Deleting is in here.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Species:</strong> Add a new bird species to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>View Owners:</strong> View all registered bird owners. Updating and Deleting is in here.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Owner:</strong> Add a new bird owner to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>View Feeds:</strong> View all types of bird feeds available at HFHR. Updating and Deleting is in here.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Add Feed:</strong> Add a new type of bird feed to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>View Feeding Logs:</strong> View all feeding log entries for bird patients. Updating and Deleting is in
        here.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Feeding Log Entry:</strong> Add a new feeding log entry for a bird patient.</li>
</ul>

